{"tid":1825522,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【恥笑！無綫未路】亞視餘孽葉家寶入侵CCTVB！","createTime":"2020-01-15T10:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T09:12:08.000Z","uid":113630,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"22dfa8930036cb1b05fcc0cb646754cc0a091d65","tid":1825522,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:54:43.000Z","msg":"【開心大發現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> CCTVB走向亞視之路？】 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eK4HrNb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeK4HrNb.png&h=779facad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住一齊shout亞洲亞洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！CCTVB行政總裁李寶安呢個亞視餘孽真係神奇，竟然同搞到亞視執笠嘅葉家寶合作，炮製極濃亞視味嘅節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：  <br />\n<br />\n泰山公德會特約 ：《癌症系列》（無綫新聞台）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />葉家寶係籌款活動總策劃 <br />\n香港浸會大學尚志會呈獻 ：《和風零食》（無綫財經資訊台）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />葉家寶係尚志會理事 <br />\n創世電視（myTV SUPER 602台）  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />葉家寶係創世電視總監  <br />\n<br />\n廣告商們，亞視嘅形象點樣大家心知肚明啦！點解仲要繼續喺亞視味越嚟越濃嘅TVB落廣告呢？ 繼續落廣告代表你哋品牌形象同亞視一樣咁柒咋喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource ：五毛電視 - 抵制tvb廣告商<br />\n**<br />\n⚡️想唔想CCTVB執笠？想就請即like &amp; share我地！愈多like廣告商愈驚😨，咁CCTVB就死得更快☠️！🤬<br />\n👉🏻&nbsp;Facebook:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.fb.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=2f68c28a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.fb.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n👉🏻&nbsp;Telegram:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=6570b85c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n👉🏻&nbsp;Instagram:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.i